    "A comprehensive analysis of different models on different tasks allows us to uncover the underlying factors that lead to performance differences between these models.After identifying the unique advantages offered by the different models, we develop ensemble learning models using the ensemble learning methods to leverage their strengths in different aspects.",
    "The first ensemble learning model involves pooling the outputs of the individual model classifiers into a deep neural network, thereby achieving an ensemble learning effect.",
    "The second ensemble learning model leverages the accuracy of the individual models as weighted votes in a voting model, following an alternative well-known approach to ensemble learning.",
